      <br><blockquote>New Arms: <a href="item.php?id=10517">Armguards of the Pestilence Priest</a>(CLR), <a href="item.php?id=10478">Lined Burlap Sleeves</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10536">Unadorned Chain Sleeves</a>. <br>New Back: <a href="item.php?id=10518">Artkeeper's Mithril Cape</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10521">Fine Seafarer's Cloak</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10510">Metal Flecked Wirespun Cape</a>. <br>New Chest: <a href="item.php?id=10530">Unadorned Breastplate</a>. <br>New Ear: <a href="item.php?id=10526">Elf Bone Snout Ring</a>. <br>New Feet: <a href="item.php?id=10527">Grimling Stockings</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10531">Unadorned Leather Boots</a>. <br>New Finger: <a href="item.php?id=10506">Half Spiked Sprocket</a>. <br>New Hands: <a href="item.php?id=10519">Brellium Platemail Gauntlets</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10522">Fine Seafarer's Gloves</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10537">Leaf Scale Gloves</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10529">Unadorned Chain Gauntlets</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10533">Unadorned Leather Gloves</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10532">Unadorned Plate Gauntlets</a>. <br>New Head: <a href="item.php?id=10514">Bellows Crafted Cap</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10520">Brellium Platemail Helm</a>. <br>New Inventory: <a href="item.php?id=10507">Archaic Circuitry</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10495">Brown Gravy</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10483">Bundle of Super Conductive Wires</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10492">Coiled Spring</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10487">Copper Node</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10500">Ethereal Parchment</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10544">Fizzy Odus Juice</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10538">Flask of Berry Juice</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10494">Freshly Cleaned Vegetables</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10541">Fungus Clump</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10539">Gnome Shaped Cookies</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10508">Golden Ember Powder</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10480">Habenero Peppers</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10545">High Quality Fish Bones</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10497">Hobgoblin Meat</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10498">Hobgolin Suprise</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10486">Innovative Clockwork Bolts</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10488">Innovative Clockwork Gears</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10504">Junk Beast Power Source</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10491">Knuckle Joint</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10485">Oxidized Steel Plate</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10489">Pinion</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10505">Rusty Servos</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10503">Saltpeter</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10484">Short Circuted Memory Storage</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10513">Silicorrosive Grease</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10481">Slarghilug Stuffed Peppers</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10512">Steel Ball Bearing</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10543">Weary Wrass in Cream</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10490">Worn Gearbox</a>. <br>New Legs: <a href="item.php?id=10525">Tae Ew Leather Leggings</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10534">Unadorned Leather Leggings</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10535">Unadorned Leather Tunic</a>. <br>New Neck: <a href="item.php?id=10515">Large Smoothmetal Torque</a>. <br>New Primary: <a href="item.php?id=10540">Astral Lance</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10528">Mace of Confusion</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10493">Pile Driver</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10542">Premier Staff of Secundae</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10502">Screamstaff</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10479">Sheetmetal Ulak</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10501">Vengeful Diamond Blade</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10499">Weighty Polearm</a>. <br>New Range: <a href="item.php?id=10509">Compound Steelshaft Bow</a>(RNG), <a href="item.php?id=10482">Planar Traveler's Manuel</a>. <br>New Secondary: <a href="item.php?id=10511">Corroded Steel Plate</a>(CLR), <a href="item.php?id=10524">Hateful Darkly Pulsing Orb</a>. <br>New Shoulders: <a href="item.php?id=10523">Fine Seafarer's Mantle</a>, <a href="item.php?id=10496">Pauldrons of Witness</a>. <br>New Waist: <a href="item.php?id=10516">Broken Drivebelt</a>. <br></blockquote></font></p>
